How can I use randomization to select three state capitals in the USA that are not in the same state or adjacent states? I have a map called states_map that contains all state capitals. The code should handle cases where there are not enough options to choose from or when all three selected capitals are from the same region of the country. Can you provide a C++ code that can accomplish this task?
