What is the most efficient way to compare two pieces of text in C++ to determine their overall sentiment and emotional tone? For example, how would I compare the phrases "I feel happy today" and "This is the worst day ever" to determine their emotional polarity? Can you provide me with a sample C++ code to perform this task? 
